二項情形，不得科以超過其特定犯罪所定最重本刑之刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CTDM/111%2c%e9%87%91%e7%b0%a1%2c309%2c20220923%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CTDM,111,金簡,309,20220923,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"金簡","JNO":"309","JDATE":"20220923","JTITLE":"洗錢防制法等"}